name: The MIT Admissions Game
description:
If the typing isn't working, try double-clicking inside the game window or refreshing the page. The keyboard disables sometimes if you click outside of the game window after starting.

I made this game specifically to supplement my MIT application. It has five levels, each of which corresponds to a different stage of my life. At the end of the game, you can "choose" to accept or deny me.

Practice typing and get to know me a little better as well!

Controls: Type. Everything is typing.

All of the code and graphics for this game are mine, but the music was found open-source online.
